snippet.title: Man Arrested By Police At Johnny Depp Amber Heard Court Case
snippet.description:
► Johnny Depp Amber Heard Court Case Man Arested

On Monday morning 20th July 2 very drunk guys just passing by and saw the crowd, outside the royal courts of justice was shouting and threatening the crowd asking for a fight with people, some people were really scared. It was really bad the 2 guys was so drunk at about 9am and stayed for about 50 minutes before police was called and arrested them. The mad thing is one of the guys was having a real go at police and you could see that they was scared to get heavy-handed to get forceful and arrest them.
#JohnnyDepp 
#JohnnyDeppIsInnocent 
#JusticeForJohnnyDepp
#JohnnyDeppDeservesJustice
